description: Deletes the specified cache report and any associated tags from the Storage Gateway database. You can only delete completed reports. If the status of the report you attempt to delete still IN-PROGRESS, the delete operation returns an error. You can use CancelCacheReport to cancel an IN-PROGRESS report.

parameters.name: CacheReportARN
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the cache report you want to delete.
